      "code": "{\"command\": \"Get-WinEvent -FilterHashtable @{LogName='System'; Id=1001; ProviderName='Microsoft-Windows-WER-SystemErrorReporting'} -MaxEvents 10 2>$null | Select-Object TimeCreated, Message | Format-List\", \"description\": \"Get all BSOD crash reports\"}",
